casebody.data:
KANSAS, petitioner,
v.
Ramiro GARCIA ; Kansas, petitioner,
v.
Donaldo Morales; and Kansas, petitioner,
v.
Guadalupe Ochoa-Lara. No. 17-834. Supreme Court of the United States March 18, 2019.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Kansas granted limited to Question 1 presented by the petition and the following question: Whether the Immigration Reform and Control Act impliedly preempts Kansas's prosecution of respondents.
